  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This trial is conducted in Asia. The aim of this trial is to compare the efficacy and safety
      of repaglinide and Glurenorm® and Glucobay® given as the mono-therapy in Chinese subjects
      being treatment-naive type 2 diabetics.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
